Ovum Woman and Child Speciality Hospitals (a unit of Neonatal Care & Research Institute Pvt Ltd) was established by a team of medical professionals with local, regional, and international experience in Paediatrics and Gynaecology. Ovum Hospitals is committed to providing high-quality, standardised, and patient-centric healthcare solutions in Maternal and Child Health. In Bangalore, we offer round-the-clock Paediatric and Maternity care, reinforcing our commitment to the health and comfort of our patients. To request deletion of your account and associated data, email us at dev@ovumhospitals.com for assistance.
